public class FusionSearchNavigableSuggestion
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<FusionSearchNavigableSuggestion>, java.io.Serializable

A Java bean representing a search term entered by the user with navigation information. This class is defined and available from model layer for transport of data to the UI layer.
